### GET /api/hello
GET https://wrait-backend.vercel.app/api/hello

###

### POST /api/register
POST https://wrait-backend.vercel.app/api/register
Content-Type: application/json
X-Proxy-Secret: your_secret_value_here
X-Device-Id: your_64_char_hex_device_id_here

###
### POST /api/transcribe
POST https://wrait-backend.vercel.app/api/transcribe
X-Proxy-Secret: SECRET_WRAIT_VALUE
X-Device-Id: a1b2c3d4e5f6789012345678901234567890abcdef1234567890abcdef123456
Content-Type: audio/wav

< tests/audio.wav

###


### POST /api/cleanup
POST https://wrait-backend.vercel.app/api/cleanup
Content-Type: application/json
X-Proxy-Secret: SECRET_WRAIT_VALUE
X-Device-Id: a1b2c3d4e5f6789012345678901234567890abcdef1234567890abcdef123478

{
  "transcript": "um, like, you know, the meeting was, uh, really productive, right? basically we covered all the points",
  "language": "en"
}
